---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/base-layout.astro";
import SiteHeader from "@components/site-header.astro";

const title = "About";
const description = "About - Programs Fall Apart";
---

<BaseLayout title={title} description={description}>
  <main id="main-content">
    <SiteHeader />
    <section>
      <div>
        <p>Hey there, I’m Amira (ah-mee-rah).</p>
        <p>
          I started in mathematics, the kind where everything is provable and
          nothing decays. Then I stumbled into software engineering, where
          everything decays and very little is provable. I stayed anyway.
        </p>

        <p>
          I don’t claim mastery over any of this. I’m a curious programmer with
          a skeptical mind and a habit of pulling on threads until the whole
          thing unravels. Most of what you’ll find here was written on those
          nights, you know the ones, when a quick fix spirals into three hours
          of asking why, and by the time you look up, the coffee beside you has
          gone cold and the room is different.
        </p>

        <p>
          This isn’t a place for answers. It’s where I write things down before
          I forget the shape of them. I’ll get things wrong. That’s part of it.
        </p>

        <p>
          If something here made you pause, even for a second, I’m a comment, an <a
            href="mailto:amira@programsfallapart.com">email</a
          >, or a <a
            href="https://twitter.com/pfa_amira"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            >twitter <span class="sr-only">(opens in new tab)</span></a
          ><sup class="footnote">*</sup> away. I’d like to know your name too.
        </p>
      </div>
      <p class="about-footnote">
        * Yes, I know it's called X now. No, I will not be calling it that.
      </p>

      <div class="credits">
        <h3>Credits</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Fonts: <a href="https://fonts.google.com/specimen/EB+Garamond" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">EB Garamond</a>, <a href="https://fonts.google.com/specimen/JetBrains+Mono" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">JetBrains Mono</a></li>
          <li>Music: classical recordings from <a href="https://www.classicals.de" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">classicals.de</a>, licensed under <a href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc/4.0/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">CC BY-NC 4.0</a></li>
          <li>Built with <a href="https://astro.build" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Astro</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about-footnote {
    font-family: "EB Garamond";
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--color-muted);
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .credits {
    margin-top: 4rem;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--color-muted);
  }

  .credits h3 {
    font-family: "JetBrains Mono", monospace;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .credits ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .credits li {
    margin-bottom: 0.35rem;
  }

  .credits a {
    color: var(--color-muted);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 3px;
  }
</style>
